    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, thanks. so if the attachment is at the VP level, the whole branch for the verb phrase just expands to include the PP? i'm having a hard time visualizing how the nodes actually connect in the hierarchy when the phrase is \"higher up\" vs tucked into the NP. can you walk me through the node connections for the VP attachment version specifically?",
