    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok i think i get the hierarchy part. but looking at the actual diagram, the branches for the PP look so separate from the main verb line. it feels like the tree gets really messy and cluttered when you have multiple attachments like that. is there a standard way to draw these to make sure the branches don't get too tangled or confusing for someone reading it?",
